    comment: '<p>To horizontally center blocks of unknown width:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-css">#horizontal-center {\n  position: absolute;\n  left: 50%;\n  transform: translateX(-50%);\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>The <code>left</code> property relates to the size of the parent so the left of child will be in the middle. The <code>transform</code> property relates to the child size. Hence it will be centered.</p>\n<p>You can check out the evolution here:</p>\n<p><?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><svg width="100%" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 800 310" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><desc>Created by HiQPdf</desc><defs></defs><g fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="1" fill-rule="evenodd" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="bevel" ></g><g fill="#596193" fill-opacity="1" stroke="none" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path vector-effect="none" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M0,0 L800,0 L800,300 L0,300 L0,0"/></g><g fill="#ffffff" fill-opacity="1" stroke="none" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path vector-effect="none" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M400,15 L700,15 L700,135 L400,135 L400,215"/></g><g fill="#596193" fill-opacity="1" stroke="#596193" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="bevel" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><text fill="#596193" fill-opacity="1" stroke="none" xml:space="preserve" x="408" y="55" font-family="&#x27;Roboto&#x27;, sans-serif" font-size="35" font-weight="400" font-style="normal" >left:50%;</text></g><g fill="#ffffff" fill-opacity="1" stroke="none" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path vector-effect="none" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M0,150 L800,150 L800,151 L0,151 L0,150"/></g><g fill="#ffffff" fill-opacity="1" stroke="none" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path vector-effect="none" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M400,1 L401,1 L401,301 L400,301 L400,1"/></g><g fill="#ffffff" fill-opacity="1" stroke="none" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path vector-effect="none" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M250,165 L550,165 L550,285 L250,285 L250,165"/></g><g fill="#596193" fill-opacity="1" stroke="#596193" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="bevel" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><text fill="#596193" fill-opacity="1" stroke="none" xml:space="preserve" x="258" y="197" font-family="&#x27;Roboto&#x27;, sans-serif" font-size="35" font-weight="400" font-style="normal" >left:50%;</text></g><g fill="#596193" fill-opacity="1" stroke="#596193" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="bevel" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><text fill="#596193" fill-opacity="1" stroke="none" xml:space="preserve" x="258" y="238" font-family="&#x27;Roboto&#x27;, sans-serif" font-size="35" font-weight="400" font-style="normal" >transform:</text></g><g fill="#596193" fill-opacity="1" stroke="#596193" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="bevel" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><text fill="#596193" fill-opacity="1" stroke="none" xml:space="preserve" x="258" y="279" font-family="&#x27;Roboto&#x27;, sans-serif" font-size="35" font-weight="400" font-style="normal" >translateX(-50%);</text></g></svg></p>\n',
